snippet.title: "Pasha Planet: Reborn" Official Game Trailler
snippet.description: Want to explore a mysterious alien planet with adorable doggie buddies? The puzzle game “Pasha Planet: Reborn,” created by a Taiwan-based indie game developer, Scorpio Game, is coming to iOS. Players are invited to enter the Underground City and experience an immersive puzzle-solving adventure unlike any other.
